## Button Replay Prevention

### Nonce in custom_id

Every `custom_id` includes a nonce to prevent replay:

```typescript
function buildCustomId(action: string, subAction: string, targetId: string): string {
  const nonce = Math.random().toString(36).substring(2, 8);
  return `${action}:${subAction}:${targetId}:${nonce}`;
}
```

### Idempotency Check

```typescript
// In button handler
const processed = await cache.get(`processed:${customId}`);
if (processed) {
  return interaction.reply({
    content: "Hành động này đã được xử lý.",
    flags: MessageFlags.Ephemeral,
  });
}

await cache.set(`processed:${customId}`, "1", { ex: 300 }); // 5 min TTL

// Process the action...
```

