## Audit Logging Requirements

### Player Actions (ActionLog)

Every player action creates a log:

```typescript
await prisma.actionLog.create({
  data: {
    characterId: character.id,
    action: "CULTIVATE",
    details: {
      mode: "STABLE",
      points: 150,
      heartDemon: 0,
    },
    publicLog: false,
  },
});
```

### Admin Actions (AdminAuditLog)

Every admin mutation creates an audit log:

```typescript
await prisma.adminAuditLog.create({
  data: {
    adminId: admin.id,
    adminRole: admin.role,
    action: "ITEM_GIVE",
    targetType: "character",
    targetId: character.id,
    targetName: character.name,
    previousValue: null,
    newValue: { itemId: "TRUC_MACH_DAN", quantity: 1 },
    reason: req.body.reason,
    evidence: req.body.evidence ?? null,
    createdAt: new Date(),
  },
});
```

### What's Logged

| Category | What to Log | What's NOT Logged |
|---------|-------------|-------------------|
| Player action | All cultivation, combat, alchemy, travel | Read-only commands |
| Admin action | All mutations: give, remove, ban, teleport, event | Read-only views |
| System action | Daily reset, seclusion complete, season | None |
| Error | Failed auth, rate limit, validation | Normal 404s |

### Log Retention

| Log Type | Retention | Storage |
|---------|----------|---------|
| AdminAuditLog | Forever | Primary DB + monthly backup |
| ActionLog | 365 days | Primary DB |
| System logs | 90 days | Log files |

